Source: tpm-reenroll
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Andrea Cervesato <thekoma@github>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/thekoma/tpm-reenroll

Package: tpm-reenroll
Architecture: all
Depends: systemd (>= 250), cryptsetup-bin, coreutils, util-linux, grep
Description: Auto re-enroll TPM2 for LUKS after PCR policy changes
 A systemd service that automatically re-enrolls TPM2 for LUKS
 when PCR policy changes, e.g. after a Secure Boot dbx update.
 Prompts for the LUKS password when re-enrollment is needed.
